description:
Food Network Star: Comeback Kitchen - Season 2, Episodes 1, 2, 3




Former finalists return to the Food Network Star kitchen for a second shot at stardom! Hosts Valerie Bertinelli and Tyler Florence kick off the proceedings by identifying what kept each of the alumni from prevailing in their previous season.

For the final challenge, the remaining four competitors battle it out for the coveted spot as the 13th finalist on the new season of Food Network Star.




Original Air Dates: 21-May-2017 to 04-Jun-2017
